rease of the average\nparticle velocity or in its suppression thus allowing a flexible control tool\nover the electron transport. Our results bring important insights into the\ndynamics of electrons floating on the surface of superfluid $^{4}$He in\nchannels with constrictions and allow an effective control over the electron\ntransport.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Jan 2014 18:13:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-03"}
