, including the near-Earth solar wind\nand low-luminosity accretion disks around black holes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Jan 2014 21:43:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Jan 2015 08:04:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
