his paper is the method\nof implementing the fuzzy decision analysis which provides a generalized fuzzy\ndecision analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Jan 2014 23:29:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-04"}
